{{Infobox football biography |name = Flamur Bajrami |image = |image_size = |caption = |fullname = Flamur Bajrami |birth_date = {{birth date and age|1997|2|10|df=y}} |birth_place = [[Mitrovica, Kosovo|Mitrovica]], [[Serbia and Montenegro|FR Yugoslavia]] |height = {{convert|1.78|m|ftin|0|abbr=on}} |position = [[Midfielder]] |currentclub = [[KF Vëllaznimi|Vëllaznimi]] |clubnumber = 23 |youthyears1 = 2010–2016 |youthclubs1 = [[KF Vëllaznimi|Vëllaznimi]] |years1 = 2016–2018 |clubs1 = [[KF Tirana|Tirana]] |caps1 = 3 |goals1 = 0 |years2 = 2018– |clubs2 = [[KF Vëllaznimi|Vëllaznimi]] |caps2 = 4 |goals2 = 0 |club-update = 19 May 2018 }} '''Flamur Bajrami''' (born 10 February 1997) is an [[Kosovo Albanian]] professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[midfielder]] for Kosovan club [[KF Vëllaznimi|Vëllaznimi]].
==Club career== In April 2014. Bajrami played in a [[Pristina]] Under-17 Regional League Tournament and was the best scorer in Group B with two goals. <ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.sportrks.com/index.aspx?SID=19&LID=2&ACatID=15&AID=6291&Ctype=1|title=Kurda me U-13 dhe U-17 dhe Prishtina me U-15 më afër titullit të Rajonit të Prishtinës|quote=Në Grupin B, me U-17. Kurda e deklasoi Prishtinën A me rezultat të thellë 4:0, kjo fitore ekipit të Kurdës i sjell edhe titullin e kampionit në Rajonin e Prishtinës me 21 pikë të tubuara. Individi më i dalluar ishte Flamur Bajrami me 2 gola të shënuar, kurse nga 1 gol shënuan, Besnik Hajdini dhe Granit Jashari që njëherësh ishte goli më i bukur në këtë takim|website=SportRKS|language=Albanian|date=14 April 2014}}</ref> In June 2015. Bajrami was at trial with the reputable [[HNK Hajduk Split Reserves and Academy|Hajduk Split B]], but didn't make the cut.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nogometplus.net/index.php/naslovna/hajduk-ii-u-opuzenu-pogledajte-tko-je-sve-na-probi-u-hajduku/|title=Hajduk II u Opuzenu: Pogledajte tko je sve na probi u Hajduku|quote=Flamur Bajrami, ofenzivac/napadač, '96 il '97 godište, iz Škole nogometa Kurda – 2013. godine izabran za najboljeg U17 igrača prištinskog rajona. Godinu mlađi, rođen 23.1.1998 je lijevo krilo (može navodno svugdje u sredini)|website=NgometPlus|language=Croatian|date=9 June 2015}}</ref>
===Tirana=== On 26 August 2016. Bajrami joined [[Albanian Superliga]] side [[KF Tirana|Tirana]].<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.botasot.info/futboll-sporti/570319/tirana-nenshkruan-me-te-riun-flamur-bajrami/|title=Tirana nënshkruan me të riun Flamur Bajrami|publisher=[[Bota Sot]]|language=Albanian|date=27 August 2016}}</ref> On 23 October 2016, he made his debut in a 2–1 away defeat against [[Luftëtari Gjirokastër]] after coming on as a substitute at 65th minute in place of [[Gjergji Muzaka]].<ref>{{cite news|url=http://fshf.org/garat/?query=info&match_id=187517|title=KS Luftëtari 2–1 KF Tirana|publisher=[[Albanian Football Association]]|language=Albanian|date=23 October 2016}}</ref>
===Vëllaznimi=== On 18 January 2018. Bajrami joined [[Football Superleague of Kosovo]] side [[KF Vëllaznimi|Vëllaznimi]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://telegrafi.com/zyrtare-fillon-epoka-cana-vellaznimi-nenshkruan-sulmuesin-flamur-bajrami/|title=Zyrtare: Fillon epoka Cana, Vëllaznimi nënshkruan me sulmuesin Flamur Bajrami|publisher=[[Telegrafi]]|language=Albanian|date=18 January 2018}}</ref>
